Mary Winefride Bousted (née Bleasdale; amuru 15 Septemba 1959) bu onye ahia ahia nke Britain bu onye okacha amara nke National Education Union (NEU) n’akuku Kevin Courtney.Bousted bụbu odeakwụkwọ ukwu nke otu ndị nkuzi, Association of Teachers and Lecturers (ATL) tupu ya na National Union of Teachers, guzobe NEU.
Bousted attended the University of Hull, gaining a BA in English
From the University of Durham (Collingwood College), she gained a PGCE. From the UCL Institute of Education she gained an MA
Later from the University of York she gained a PhD.
Bousted kụziri Bekee site na 1982 ruo 1987 na Bentley Wood High School na Harrow
Site na 1988 ruo 1991 ọ bụ Onye isi nke Bekee na Whitmore High School na Harrow.
